<item>
            <title>[IO-857] PathUtils.cleanDirectory method does not erase subdirectories</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/IO-857</link>
                <project id="12310477" key="IO">Commons IO</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The PathUtils.cleanDirectory method does not erase subdirectories. Only the files in them. The FileUtils.cleanDirectory method erases everything except the directory itself, and this is the expected behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13583037">IO-857</key>
            <summary>PathUtils.cleanDirectory method does not erase subdirectories</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
